{"tid":1532070,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣西每個閘口有2~5個職員守住，跳唔到閘！","createTime":"2019-09-02T12:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T14:08:00.000Z","uid":193592,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"89e4c44243bddafdb387669699e161269d3777cf","tid":1532070,"uid":193592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:04:58.000Z","msg":"荃灣西鐵站每個閘口有2~5個黨鐵職員守住，跳唔到閘，話去補飛都一定要收錢先比補（真係要補既大家記住講最近既站！！）<br />\n<br />\n其實佢怕我地跳每個閘口要放多幾個人睇住成本都好高，繼續由佢地放人喺到！真係跳唔到咪罷搭囉！高啲既巴絲直頭可以唔洗去閘口都跨到欄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上都唔敢做既都可以買小童飛！同埋<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好再喺任何黨鐵站商店消費！</strong></span>仲有以下既黨鐵商場：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">圓方<br />\n德福廣場<br />\n青衣城<br />\nPopCorn<br />\n綠楊坊<br />\nCitylink<br />\n杏花新城<br />\n連理街<br />\n海趣坊<br />\n駿景廣場<br />\n新屯門商場<br />\n恒福商場</span><br />\n<br />\n和勇一齊做！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港！時代革命！<br />\n五大訴求！缺一不可！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"bdcb7fe1c58199d1734856789aef5061140f909b","tid":1532070,"uid":21319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:05:36.000Z","msg":"如果你英文好的話 請以後發言中英對照 please recap ur comment in English<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1531632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1531632</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0e7ba1a15c79e0c38f27d88b2c8bbb6c75df1ee2","tid":1532070,"uid":80125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:06:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4aca112d5a21975b44ca4ecf54bd48d7c93a0e3","tid":1532070,"uid":193592,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0e7ba1a15c79e0c38f27d88b2c8bbb6c75df1ee2","tid":1532070,"uid":80125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89e4c44243bddafdb387669699e161269d3777cf","tid":1532070,"uid":193592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:04:58.000Z","msg":"荃灣西鐵站每個閘口有2~5個黨鐵職員守住，跳唔到閘，話去補飛都一定要收錢先比補（真係要補既大家記住講最近既站！！）<br />\n<br />\n其實佢怕我地跳每個閘口要放多幾個人睇住成本都好高，繼續由佢地放人喺到！真係跳唔到咪罷搭囉！高啲既巴絲直頭可以唔洗去閘口都跨到欄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上都唔敢做既都可以買小童飛！同埋<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好再喺任何黨鐵站商店消費！</strong></span>仲有以下既黨鐵商場：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">圓方<br />\n德福廣場<br />\n青衣城<br />\nPopCorn<br />\n綠楊坊<br />\nCitylink<br />\n杏花新城<br />\n連理街<br />\n海趣坊<br />\n駿景廣場<br />\n新屯門商場<br />\n恒福商場</span><br />\n<br />\n和勇一齊做！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港！時代革命！<br />\n五大訴求！缺一不可！</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:06:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:10:56.000Z","msg":"之前冇架<br />\n不過你估佢地咁放人喺到成本要幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地轉搭其他車，如果團結罷搭令佢少左收入佢又要繼續放咁多人喺到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a40f4380075827ff2f824476a7d43074784e75","tid":1532070,"uid":80125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:12:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"827bd6ad8c77006b3f4e033da989987350914a34","tid":1532070,"uid":193592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3a40f4380075827ff2f824476a7d43074784e75","tid":1532070,"uid":80125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4aca112d5a21975b44ca4ecf54bd48d7c93a0e3","tid":1532070,"uid":193592,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0e7ba1a15c79e0c38f27d88b2c8bbb6c75df1ee2","tid":1532070,"uid":80125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:06:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:10:56.000Z","msg":"之前冇架<br />\n不過你估佢地咁放人喺到成本要幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as